text: Kimberly Kay (born 20 September 1989) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2011 World Aquatics Championships, 2013 World Aquatics Championships, and 2015 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
